ai.grakn.concept

Interface Resource<D>

  • Type Parameters:
    D - The data type of this resource type. Supported Types include: String, Long, Double, and Boolean
    All Superinterfaces:
    Comparable<Concept>, Concept, Instance

    public interface Resource<D>
extends Instance

    Represent a literal resource in the graph.

    Acts as an Instance when relating to other instances except it has the added functionality of: 1. It is unique to its ResourceType based on it's value. 2. It has a ResourceType.DataType associated with it which constrains the allowed values.

    Author:
    fppt
